<h2 class="page-headline">ItemView Component</h2>
<p>
    The <code>ItemView</code> component has to be used as container for all other components.
    Components are added directly on the view with the <code>add</code> method.
</p>
<p>
    Usage:
    <code>
        view = new Backbone.Marionette.Component.ItemView()
        view.add new TextFieldItemView(â€¦)
    </code>
</p>

